              At the <a href="https://nli.org.il">National Library of Israel</a>, our product team kept the site updated, usable, and engaging. I worked on site architecture, search engine improvements, and new content pages, prioritizing SEO and usability. These efforts brought 3M additional users to the platform.
          </p>
